lid. In an appendix, Karen E. Smith uses the solidity of\nabsolute integral closures to characterize the test ideal for a large class of\nGorenstein domains of prime characteristic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2020 18:10:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-22"}
